ygData.messageBody:
I have nearly 30K in the bank, and a lot of stuff
to trade. I have Cobalt Gaunts, and Helm, Singing
Steel Boots and Gaunts. If anyone is on the Karana
server give Seffar a tell. <br><br>What I am looking for
is various peices of Mrylokar's Armor (class
specific rogue armor, pretty much equiv to Cobalt, Singing
Steel etc.)<br>FBSS, Slime Coated Harpoon, you
know..the works. I'll consider all HIGH-END rogue
items.<br><br>Sereth/Seffar/Mindaan<br>Level 51 Cavalier<br>Level 28 Magi<br>Level 25 Rogue
